data.description: A wonderful 3 Bdrm 2.5 Ba home on American lake with 43' of no bank peble beach waterfront. This 2,600 +/- SF home has a bright kitchen with nook, a spacious living/dining room combo with access to two large decks and wonderful view of American lake. The upper floor has two bedrooms with the main bedroom having a great view of the lake with views of fabulous sunsets and morning sunrises. The lower floor offers a  bedroom, bathroom with large shower and living room with kitchenette and has nice views of the lake and backyard. The property has an additional building that has 400 SF of living space and an attached two car garage. This could also be a future accessory dwelling unit. The property is gated and fully fenced. Two minutes to I-5.
